  "detailed_description": "The story happened a long time later, and under the curse, the sea swallowed up the land!<br />\r\nHuman civilization is gone!<br />\r\nUndead creatures breed and regenerate in the ocean!<br />\r\nYou will be the last human to find the last piece of land!<br />\r\n----<br />\r\nWhat should you do on this last piece of land?<br />\r\nCan you escape the evil spirit's claws?<br />\r\nCan you survive?<br />\r\nCan you save more compatriots?<br />\r\n---<br />\r\nMore unknown, waiting for you<br />\r\n---<br />\r\nGame play<br />\r\nBattle: Kill the Undead to gain resources<br />\r\nBuild: Build your own safe house<br />\r\nPlanting: A necessary item for survival<br />\r\nLivestock raising:<br />\r\nwait<br />\r\n----<br />\r\nThe most important thing is: Live",
